    "causal_summary": "The shared post-mutation hook (`runPostMutationHooks`) clears trigger, tool, constitutional, graph-signal, degree, and co-activation caches but never invalidates the entity-density cache, so after a `memoryupdate` renames a high-degree memory or rewrites its trigger phrases, graph-channel routing keeps matching stale tokens until the 60s TTL lapses",
